  "body": "I build Geth server images by checking out the repo at a git branch/tag rather than using Docker. With this approach, I cannot build images at a stable version, rather have to lock to version or use master (unstable).\r\n\r\nProposal is to have a stable git tag like there is in Docker:\r\n```\r\nethereum/client-go:stable\r\n```\r\n\r\nSo I can then build from source by running:\r\n```\r\ngit clone --branch stable --depth 1 https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum.git\r\ncd go-ethereum\r\nmake geth\r\n```",
